---
layout: layouts/base-preview.njk
title: "Disability Resources by Category"
description: "Browse disability resources for caregivers and families by category — therapy, adaptive equipment, respite care, financial help, and more, in every U.S. state."
permalink: /preview/resources/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="py-12 section-warm">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Find Resources</h1>
    <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
      Pick a category to browse trusted programs, services, and organizations for individuals with disabilities and their caregivers — then filter by your state or city.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
      {% for cat in categories | sort(attribute='label') %}
      {% set catCount = (directory | filterByTopCategory(cat.value)).length %}
      {% if catCount > 0 %}
      <a href="/preview/resources/{{ cat.value }}/" class="card px-4 py-3 no-underline flex items-center justify-between gap-2" style="color: var(--color-text);">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold leading-snug" style="color: var(--color-primary);">{{ cat.label }}</h2>
        <span class="tag text-xs shrink-0" style="background-color: var(--color-warm); color: var(--color-primary);">{{ catCount }}</span>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- Submit CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Know a Resource We're Missing?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Help us grow our directory by submitting resources you know about.</p>
      <a href="/submit-resource/" class="btn-primary no-underline">Submit a Resource</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
